  "title": "Facilities Technician (HVAC/ACMV, Class 2B/3, Night Shift)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Carry out nightly checks and basic servicing of air‑conditioning units and school facilities.</li><li>Identify and report any defects or safety concerns in classrooms, shared areas, and outdoor spaces.</li><li>Manage urgent maintenance tasks, including electrical issues, plumbing repairs, and minor facility rectifications.</li><li>Support contractors during repair or upgrade works when required.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Possess valid <strong>Class 2B/3 License</strong></li><li>Nitec in Mechanical, Electrical, or Building Services or equivalent.</li><li>At least 3 years of <strong>hands‑on facility maintenance </strong>experience; candidates with 5 years of <strong>building or construction maintenance </strong>experience.</li><li><strong>Able to work night shift (10pm - 7am)</strong></li><li>Practical knowledge in<strong> air‑conditioning maintenance </strong>plus basic competencies in electrical and plumbing troubleshooting.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R21100996</p>",
